The Zondo commission of inquiry into state capture is hearing testimony from Eskom officials Snehal Nagar and Gert Opperman on the “unlawful” prepayment Eskom made to Gupta owned Tegeta to buy Optimum coal mine. JOHANNESBURG - The Zondo commission of inquiry into state capture is hearing testimony from Eskom officials Snehal Nagar and Gert Opperman on the “unlawful” prepayment Eskom made to Gupta-owned Tegeta to buy Optimum coal mine. WATCH: Zondo Commission hears about Eskom payments to Tegeta 